### **How to Verify**
1.  **Run `app.py`**.
2.  **Send MQTT Data:** Use an MQTT client to publish `{"id": "Truck-1", "temp": 20, "humidity": 50}` to `supply_chain/truck1/telemetry`.
3.  **Check Database:** The `tracking_data.db` file will be created and populated with this data.
4.  **Check Frontend:** The `tracking.html` page (if open) will update with this sensor data.